# Canonical site origin (no trailing slash). Required for production
# builds — og:image, twitter:image, and og:url need absolute URLs or
# social crawlers (FB / X / LinkedIn / Slack / Discord / KakaoTalk)
# silently fail the preview. Copy this file to `.env.local` for local
# overrides, or set the variable directly in your deploy environment.
#
# The service-detail VIEW-COUNT BADGE (hits.sh) also derives from this — it
# counts under this URL's host. Unset (pre-deploy) → the badge is hidden,
# avoiding a "0 views" badge before there's any traffic.
# PRIVACY: when set, each detail-page visit requests an SVG from hits.sh,
# which sends the visitor's IP to that third party.
VITE_SITE_URL=https://your-domain.example
